                                    aligned</p>
                            </handNote>
                        </handDesc>
                        <!--  *************************************  <decoDesc>  *********************************  -->
                        <decoDesc>
                            <decoNote>
                                <ab>Linear frame decorated at the top and the bottom by dotted zigzag pattern, and
                                    on the left side by a serpentine motif</ab>
                                <locus>Surrounding text and symbols. The right side is totally faded</locus>
                            </decoNote>
                            <decoNote>
                                <ab>Seven-branched candelabrum</ab>
                                <locus>Below the inscription, in the center</locus>
                            </decoNote>
                            <decoNote>
                                <ab>The word: shalom</ab>
                                <locus>Flanking the candelabrum on the left and right sides at top</locus>
                            </decoNote>
                            <decoNote>
                                <ab>Ram's horn</ab>
                                <locus>Flanking the candelabrum on the left side below the word:  "shalom"</locus>
                            </decoNote>
                            <decoNote>
                                <ab>Citron</ab>
                                <locus>To the left of the candelabrum, below the ram's horn</locus>
                            </decoNote>
                            <decoNote>
                                <ab>Two birds facing left</ab>
                                <locus>One to the left of the candelabrum, below the citron, and one on the other
                                    side of the candelabrum</locus>
                            </decoNote>
                            <decoNote>
                                <ab>Unidentifiable symbols</ab>
                                <locus>To the right of the candelabrum</locus>
                            </decoNote>
